title: Beyond 5 Senses - ET Contactees
description:
BEYOND FIVE SENSES explores these questions through the very personal experiences of three Santa Fe women who struggle with their own placement in the world regarding their own self identities, and how they have been transformed as a result of their having come into direct contact with extraterrestrials. This film relates their challenges of how to successfully express their experiences in hopes of contributing to an elevated planetary consciousness, and facilitate healing and growth in their own lives, and the lives they touch.

Insightful and whimsical commentary is included in the film by some of the planet&#039;s eminent leaders in the field(s) of metaphysics, astrophysics and ET documentation to engage, enlighten and provoke the view to consider all possibilities. BEYOND FIVE SENSES promises a moving experience for even the least traveled viewer in a benevolent, thought provoking sojourn through the sensory dimension.
